  "text": "In present paper, we study the method of apply naturalistic driving films in the focus group discussion to discover drivers' needs. To make the study more focus, we consider the 3D sound presentation of traffic environment as the information presentation modality. [CITATION_1] indicated that a strong positive support that the design of using natural sound to present the traffic situation to the truck drivers in 3 dimensions. It is not clear that if it is a useful way of presenting information to personal vehicle as well. At the same time, there are many design questions about what the driver needs is and what information in the traffic should to be presented, how to design the sound, should the sound information represent the location or movement of the road objects and at what time frame, etc, that one need to answer.",
